name: Victoria Sonnerati
description:
--Fig08--

Victoria Sonnerati is a Scrofa Galliforme creature from Tadmor, an exoplanet located 45 light years from earth.
The individuals live in enormous muddy plains and the genders differ in shape and structure. While the males reach only 1 meter in height, females can grow up to an enormous 3,5 meters. Among the males, there can be only one female on the flock, so they will fight to protect its territory.
